<span class="p">}</span>

<span class="c1">// еӯ—з¬ҰдёІдёӯеҸҢеӨ§жӢ¬еҸ·еҠ `\`жҳҜдёәдәҶйҳІжӯўжЁЎжқҝиҜӯжі•еҶІзӘҒпјҢеңЁе®һйҷ…д»Јз ҒдёӯиҰҒеҺ»жҺү`\`</span>
<span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">жҲ‘еҸ«</span><span class="se">\</span><span class="s1">{</span><span class="se">\</span><span class="s1">{name</span><span class="se">\</span><span class="s1">}</span><span class="se">\</span><span class="s1">}пјҢжҳҜдҪҚ</span><span class="se">\</span><span class="s1">{</span><span class="se">\</span><span class="s1">{position</span><span class="se">\</span><span class="s1">}</span><span class="se">\</span><span class="s1">}</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">render</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">userInfo</span><span class="p">);</span> <span class="c1">// жҲ‘еҸ«BetterпјҢжҳҜдҪҚfront-end engineer</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="е°Ҹж•°еҸ–ж•ҙ">е°Ҹж•°еҸ–ж•ҙ</h2>

<div class="language-js highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kd">var</span> <span class="nx">num</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mf">123.123</span>

